      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; parameter mapping between simulation and experiment is documented.",
      "rationale": "At Model Risk Level 2, formal equivalency assessment of all input parameters between the validation experiments and the COU is not required. The primary input parameters (geometry, flow rate, rotational speed, fluid viscosity) have been matched to within stated tolerances as documented in the test conditions factor assessment above."
